      "message": "Patch Set 4: Verified\n\nThe build works:\nhttp://new-jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-388?focusedCommentId=15689&page=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.issuetabpanels:comment-tabpanel#comment-15689",
